257
00:25:43,583 --> 00:25:48,884
- Osmanthus or green bean?
- Whichever. We can ask for more.

258
00:25:50,444 --> 00:25:53,204
I can hardly make choice,
especially when it comes to food.

259
00:25:55,884 --> 00:25:59,523
