we set up a stage in a real place.

276
00:27:17,123 --> 00:27:22,323
A first for Feishao and Wang Ke too.
Performing live in a real setting.

277
00:27:23,724 --> 00:27:25,724
I can hardly wait.

278
00:27:32,684 --> 00:27:38,204
(I can't get a word in.
