and the other harmonizes there♪

290
00:29:30,724 --> 00:29:35,803
♪The other harmonizes there♪

291
00:29:37,244 --> 00:29:47,164
♪The song is like the river in spring♪

292
00:29:47,164 --> 00:29:57,404
